      <h1>Forskrift om endring i forskrift om m&#xE5;ling av petroleum for fiskale form&#xE5;l og for beregning av CO<sub>2</sub> -avgift</h1>
      <section class="section" data-name="kapI" id="kapittel-1" data-lovdata-URL="LTI/forskrift/2008-11-24-1253/KAPITTEL_1">
        <h2 data-text-align="center">I</h2>
        <article class="legalP" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1">I forskrift 1. november 2001 nr. 1234 om m&#xE5;ling av petroleum for fiskale form&#xE5;l og for beregning av CO<sub>2</sub> -avgift gj&#xF8;res f&#xF8;lgende endring:</article>
        <article class="defaultP" margin-top="true">I &#xAB;Referanseliste&#xBB; skal henvisningene;<ul class="defaultList"><li><article class="listArticle" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1-punkt-1"><article class="legalP" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1-punkt-1-ledd-1">NORSOK I-104, Fiscal measurement system for hydrocarbon gas (Rev 2, 2 June 1998)</article></article></li><li><article class="listArticle" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1-punkt-2"><article class="legalP" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1-punkt-2-ledd-1">NORSOK I-105, Fiscal measurement system for hydrocarbon liquid (Rev 2, 2 June 1998)</article></article></li></ul></article>
        <article class="defaultP" margin-top="true">endres til;<ul class="defaultList"><li><article class="listArticle" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1-punkt-3"><article class="legalP" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1-punkt-3-ledd-1">NORSOK I-104, Fiscal measurement systems for hydrocarbon gas (nov. 2005)</article></article></li><li><article class="listArticle" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1-punkt-4"><article class="legalP" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1-punkt-4-ledd-1">NORSOK I-105, Fiscal measurement systems for hydrocarbon liquid (aug. 2007)</article></article></li></ul></article>
      </section>
      <section class="section" data-name="kapII" id="kapittel-2" data-lovdata-URL="LTI/forskrift/2008-11-24-1253/KAPITTEL_2">
        <h2 data-text-align="center">II</h2>
        <article class="legalP" id="kapittel-2-ledd-1">Endringen trer i kraft 1. januar 2009.</article>
      </section>
